creator: Inteleon AB
descriptionHtml:
With SMS Park you pay quickly and easily for your parking all over Sweden. Forget all about coins and avoid queuing at the parking meter. Download the app and park directly - you are up and running in minutes. You pay in arrears by invoice or debit or credit card.

KEY FEATURES
• Quick and easy parking at the press of a button
• Find the nearest parking through the app's map
• Save money by paying for the exact parking time
• Release stress and say goodbye to parking fines. Extend your parking time wherever you are
• Simple business solution for the entire company

HOW IT WORKS
• Register in three simple steps
• Select vehicle and car park
• Select end time. Extend if you want
• Press Start
• Select your preferred payment option

You can change your end time at any time or end the parking to pay only for the time you park, even if you don't know in advance. By changing your end time, you don't need to stress or worry about parking fines.

Parking guards will see in their PDAs that you paid your parking with SMS Park. The app works on all car parks that have a SMS Park sign or decal.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: Supports moving your account to EasyPark.
